 line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">What starts as a minor disagreemen=
t gets amplified into completely opposing worldviews. What starts as a nuan=
ced conversation gets boiled down to catchphrases. Those who start as your =
opponents become your enemies.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">It&#8217;s easy t=
o get worked up if you focus on the extremes, on the teams tugging the rope=
