 it&#8217;s used to describe how ideas enter the mainstream conversation wh=
ere they influence public opinion, societal norms, and institutional practi=
ces.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The Overton Window is the knot in the narra=
