r more palatable.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 1=
6px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">The same thing happens with na=
rratives, but instead of one company carefully setting prices to maximize t=
he likelihood that you buy the Pro tier, independent and opposed teams, oft=
