oup chats and memes, somehow figure out how to pull hard enough that they m=
ove the knot back to what they view as an acceptable place. It&#8217;s a ki=
nd of cultural magic when you think about it.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: r=
gb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Th=
ere are a lot of examples I could use to illustrate the idea, many of which=
 could get me in trouble, so I&#8217;ll stick to what I know: tech. Specifi=
cally, degrowth vs. growth, or EA vs. e/acc.&#160;</p><h3 class=3D"header-w=
ith-anchor-widget" style=3D"-moz-appearance: optimizelegibility; -moz-osx-f=
